data.description: One of the larger home floor plans in the desirable Settler's Glen community in Waxahachie. The large 4 bedroom, 2.1 bath home has dramatic tall ceilings in the spacious large living & dining room and is perfect for entertaining large gatherings! 2 areas for eating, a dining bar plus a breakfast nook in the kitchen area! The large kitchen has tons of cabinets, granite counters, & stainless appliances. The great home has been refreshed with a full repaint, some new flooring, & a newly landscaped front yard.  The primary bedroom is secluded on the 1st floor with a large ensuite bath & extra counter space, across from a generous utility room. All secondary bedrooms are on the 2nd floor and there is a seating or study nook off the hallway. Settlers Glen has a community park with a playground, & a picnic area with grills  Just 30 minutes south of Dallas off of I-35, Waxahachie features a charming historic downtown square filled with, restaurants, shops, dining, and entertainment. Wonderful!
